about.summary: Standard components for automated data processing with Zocalo at Diamond Light Source

name: zocalo-dls
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "zocalo-dls" %}
{% set version = "0.2.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/zocalo_dls-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: "c31dccec0732985d81181629a49b0afb025c55cf0c0eb1aadaaa15bc83f0f592"

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv "
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - ispyb
    - procrunner
    - python
    - setuptools
    - zocalo

test:
  imports:
    - zocalo_dls
    - zocalo_dls.service
    - zocalo_dls.wrapper

about:
  home: "https://github.com/DiamondLightSource/python-zocalo-dls"
  license: "BSD-3-Clause"
  license_family: "BSD"
  license_file: "LICENSE"
  summary: "Standard components for automated data processing with Zocalo at Diamond Light Source"
  doc_url: "https://python-zocalo-dls.readthedocs.io/en/latest/"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - tschoonj
    - Anthchirp
